{"name":"Sesame Ginger Nourish Bowl","slug":"sesame-ginger-nourish-bowl","description":"<p>Prep rice in the <a data-item-id=\"bd092c36-a4ba-5b73-9abc-fa95c0102e9a\" href=\"\">Multipurpose</a> or <a data-item-id=\"38e9c45d-465e-4a8b-8c16-5f437f361347\" href=\"\">Round Steamer </a>– it's fast &amp; convenient. You can make these bowls ahead of time and you’ve got an easy, fresh, and healthy go-to for the week. The Sesame Ginger Dressing adds nuttiness, richness and a small zesty kick to pairs perfectly with steak and rice. &nbsp;</p>","ingredients":[{"name":"cooked rice","quantity":"3 cups","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"corn kernels or baby corn","quantity":"2 cups","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"veggies, your choice, cooked or raw","quantity":"4 cups","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"leftover steak","quantity":"1 lb (450 g)","additionalInstruction":"sliced thinly against the grain"},{"name":"Sesame Ginger Dressing","quantity":"<sup>3</sup>&frasl;<sub>4</sub> cup prepared","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"Sesame Ginger Dressing Mix","quantity":"2 tbsp","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"low sodium soy sauce or gluten free soy sauce","quantity":"3 tbsp","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"oil","quantity":"<sup>1</sup>&frasl;<sub>3</sub> cup","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"rice vinegar","quantity":"<sup>1</sup>&frasl;<sub>2</sub> cup","additionalInstruction":null}],"totalTime":"5 min","servings":"4 servings","preparation":"<ol>\n  <li>Arrange first four ingredients in four serving bowls.</li>\n  <li>Drizzle with dressing.</li>\n  <li>Sprinkle with toppings, if desired.&nbsp;</li>\n</ol>","tags":[{"slug":"beef","name":"Beef"},{"slug":"dinner","name":"Dinner"},{"slug":"lunch","name":"Lunch"},{"slug":"chinese_new_year","name":"Lunar New Year"},{"slug":"low_sodium","name":"Low-sodium"},{"slug":"gluten_free_e8446d0","name":"Gluten-free"},{"slug":"high_protein","name":"High Protein"},{"slug":"sugar_conscious","name":"Sugar Conscious"},{"slug":"dairy_free","name":"Dairy-free"},{"slug":"no_cook","name":"No-Cook"},{"slug":"one_dish","name":"One Dish"}],"nutritionalInformation":{"servingSize":"","calories":540,"fat":20,"saturatedFat":5,"transFat":0,"cholesterol":45,"sodium":260,"carbohydrate":58,"fiber":6,"sugars":7,"protein":34},"tips":"<p>Swap <a data-item-id=\"da3fc3f1-5182-4f24-9a25-3e38acdbc892\" href=\"\">Rotisserie Chicken</a> or 5–6 oz (150–170 g) firm tofu for steak.</p>\n<p>Add 1 tsp <a href=\"https://epicure.com/en-ca/category/broths\">Broth Mix</a> for each cup of water to layer complex flavour in your pasta, grains, and pulses.</p>","perfectlyBalanceYourPlate":"<p>This is a perfectly balanced plate.</p>"}